data.description: Certified Pre-owned Home is Back on the Market. Inspection report, septic report and roof report provided and Home Warranty Provided. This charming home offers 1.77 acres, 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, lower level walk out with bar and wood burning stove, lots of storage in basement, and fenced area. AC, Water softener, refrigerator, microwave, and gas range all have been replaced in the last 3-5 years. Hall Bath remodel was done by Bath Fitter about 3 years ago. 13 x 9 Master  Spa H2X 2019 Swim Spa, Hardwood Floors in some areas. Garage has separate gas heater and thermostat. Two patios and front covered porch. Schedule your showing now! Agents read A2A Remarks.
